      "date": "2013-09-20 05:07:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d54e7d5a-21ad-11e3-afee-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
