      },
      "date": "2013-11-21 10:47:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a7230058-5291-11e3-935d-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
